io.soliton.protobuf.json

Class JsonResponseFuture<V extends Message>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractFuture<V>
      • io.soliton.protobuf.json.JsonResponseFuture<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of this promise.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ListenableFuture<V>, Future<V>

    public final class JsonResponseFuture<V extends Message>
extends AbstractFuture<V>
    Represents a handle on the result of the invocation of a method over JSON-RPC.

    This implementation is in charge of marshalling the response received from the server into the expected protobuf type.

    Author:
    Julien Silland (julien@soliton.io)
